00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:49,640
 where we're singing and praising, we can lift our hands,

122
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:51,640
 we can kneel down on the floor, right?

123
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:53,920
 If you've been in church for a while,

124
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,840
 you probably know how to speak Christianese, right?

