00:35:33,040 --> 00:35:35,960
 He lived among us, He healed us,

778
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:38,280
 He fed us, He served us,

779
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:40,760
 He washed our feet, He embraced us,

780
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:44,680
 He invites us, He spoke up for us,

781
00:35:44,680 --> 00:35:48,000
 and ultimately He went to the cross to die for you,

782
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:50,320
 to show you His love.

783
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:53,480
 He put His love into action.

784
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:56,800
 And He loves you so much

785
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:58,680
 that He perfectly lived on this earth

786
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:02,660
 to tell us what an active faith looks like.

787
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:06,260
 He knows you too well to be content

788
00:36:06,260 --> 00:36:07,880
 just to watch you waste your life

789
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:10,580
 by not putting your faith into action.

790
00:36:11,420 --> 00:36:13,180
 And when Jesus comes back,

791
00:36:13,180 --> 00:36:16,580
 He's looking for those who are truly faithful.

792
00:36:16,580 --> 00:36:18,460
 Is this what He's going to find

793
00:36:18,460 --> 00:36:20,940
 when He comes back for this church?

794
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:24,900
 Is this what He's gonna find when He looks at your life?

795
00:36:24,900 --> 00:36:30,820
 So I'm gonna ask you to close your eyes for a moment, church,

796
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:33,420
 and just think about those things for a minute.

797
00:36:33,420 --> 00:36:37,620
 I know it's been hard, and you know,

798
00:36:38,140 --> 00:36:43,140
 we've been wrestling a lot with the book of James

799
00:36:43,140 --> 00:36:46,840
 as we prepared this.

800
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:53,500
 And in this beautiful gathering of God's children

801
00:36:53,500 --> 00:36:56,000
 who make up this community,

802
00:36:56,000 --> 00:37:00,060
 and as God has called us into the uncharted,

803
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:04,000
 He's calling us into action.

804
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:07,500
 [congregation murmuring]

805
00:37:07,500 --> 00:37:13,440
 And like I said, all this is rooted.

806
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,440
 This is not a guilt trip.

807
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:19,200
 This is not a bashing over your head.

808
00:37:19,200 --> 00:37:22,260
 At least I hope not.

809
00:37:22,260 --> 00:37:28,420
 But this is a reminder of the love that God had for you.

810
00:37:30,740 --> 00:37:35,620
 This is a reminder of the potential that lives in you.

811
00:37:35,620 --> 00:37:42,340
 That God, the plans that God in mind when He created you,

812
00:37:42,340 --> 00:37:45,460
 when He knitted you together in your mother's womb,

813
00:37:45,460 --> 00:37:50,880
 that He had a plan and a purpose for you to live out.

814
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:58,020
 And for sure, that's one that includes obedience to Him,

815
00:38:00,100 --> 00:38:02,540
 of doing things in the sake of His name

816
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:06,240
 that you never thought you'd able to experience or see.

817
00:38:06,240 --> 00:38:10,220
 But because you allowed God's love

818
00:38:10,220 --> 00:38:12,580
 and power to work through you,

819
00:38:12,580 --> 00:38:14,600
 you bring honor and praise to Him,

820
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:16,660
 and life to others by doing that.

821
00:38:16,660 --> 00:38:23,260
 And like I said just now, Jesus loves us too much

822
00:38:23,260 --> 00:38:26,780
 to let us just be content with this comfy,

823
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:29,980
 cozy Christianity that is so easy to embrace.

824
00:38:30,900 --> 00:38:33,820
 (soft piano music)

825
00:38:33,820 --> 00:38:38,700
 But rather, it's this life-changing,

826
00:38:38,700 --> 00:38:40,620
 radical obedience to God

827
00:38:40,620 --> 00:38:46,220
 that will bring salvation to you and those around us,

828
00:38:46,220 --> 00:38:50,220
 that declares God's kingdom on earth as it is in heaven.

829
00:38:50,220 --> 00:38:53,980
 And so, Jesus, we pray.

830
00:38:53,980 --> 00:38:59,380
 If I could be so bold on praying

831
00:38:59,380 --> 00:39:01,100
 on behalf of my brothers and sisters,

832
00:39:01,100 --> 00:39:04,060
 that we would not be content just to have a faith

833
00:39:04,060 --> 00:39:07,960
 that's based upon lip service,

834
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:10,620
 that's based upon a few songs

835
00:39:10,620 --> 00:39:12,520
 that we might sing every now and then,

836
00:39:12,520 --> 00:39:16,580
 but it's a life of obedience.

837
00:39:16,580 --> 00:39:26,700
 It's a life that's constantly looking out for ways

838
00:39:26,700 --> 00:39:28,580
 that we can show your love to others,

839
00:39:28,580 --> 00:39:29,700
 no matter who they are,

840
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:34,100
 knowing as we saw in the video earlier,

841
00:39:34,100 --> 00:39:36,140
 that your grace is sufficient for us,

842
00:39:36,140 --> 00:39:41,300
 that even if it's the most challenging, mind-boggling,

843
00:39:41,300 --> 00:39:43,080
 not-make-sense thing to this world

844
00:39:43,080 --> 00:39:44,480
 that you've called us to do,

845
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:48,180
 that we will have the faith to put that into action

846
00:39:48,180 --> 00:39:50,980
 and do it anyway, knowing you'll meet us where we are,

847
00:39:50,980 --> 00:39:52,420
 that you'll never leave us abandoned,

848
00:39:52,420 --> 00:39:54,540
 that you'll never leave us or forsake us,

849
00:39:54,540 --> 00:39:56,620
 that we have a helper in the Holy Spirit.

850
00:39:57,380 --> 00:39:59,620
 (gentle music)

851
00:39:59,620 --> 00:40:01,020
 And we have the most high God

852
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:04,380
 who fights every battle on our behalf.

853
00:40:04,380 --> 00:40:12,780
 So Jesus, make this our hearts, our lives.

854
00:40:12,780 --> 00:40:18,420
 May we be your good and faithful servants,

855
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:22,100
 sons and daughters, as we live out our life in this world,

856
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:26,380
 truly worshiping you with everything we have.

